paragraphs.text: Hannah beats out Russell Westbrook for NBA MVP.

That was gold, Lindsay Zoladz. Peggy’s workmanlike respect for the craft and connection with the audience sprinkled with just enough Ginsberg insanity to make it sing. I think you’ve discovered the cure for the common list entry.

d0e6283ae710.title: We find out that Hannah fantasized the entire show; she is a waitress serving the rest of the…

paragraphs.text: We find out that Hannah fantasized the entire show; she is a waitress serving the rest of the characters at brunch. After they finish eating, she follows Marnie home, kills her and drinks her blood to gain her power.

paragraphs.text: They all go to Burning Man, but it turns out it was a ruse to lure Hannah inside the Burning Man, and she’s sacrificed to the ascended spirit of Steve Jobs.

49745a89270a.title: Hannah gets hit by a bus in the opening minutes.

paragraphs.name: d6be
paragraphs.text: Hannah gets hit by a bus in the opening minutes. The camera slowly surveys the surroundings of a busy New York street, horns honking and birds chirping. It finally focuses on Hannah, laying motionlessly on the street, bleeding out for the remaining 29 minutes.
